data.expected_result: You jump to the message, even if was deleted
data.short_description: Discord crashes when attempting to jump to deleted messages in Search. Note: Crashes appear to occur sporadically, similar to the Audit Log crashes, so this could take several attempts.
data.steps_to_repro: - Open Search & search for "From: <you>" - Delete some older messages that are separate from each other so you can jump - Attempt jumping to the deleted messages
